data.description:
Looking for the best deal in Grovetown under $500k? Well, how about this almost 4,400 sq ft beauty in immaculate condition offering 5 Bedrooms (3 of which are ensuite while two are a Jack n Jill), 4.5 Bathrooms, a  spacious step-up theater room fully fitted with a projector and large screen, new carpets throughout, freshly painted walls, a two-car garage, an additional driveway space to park up to a total of 5 cars, and a 12ft by 8ft shed to remain in the fenced yard!

I ran out of breath typing all of that but there's more! This is the very desirable Barrington floor plan which offers a very open floor plan with an extremely large kitchen that opens up into the great room and wood-burning fireplace. Very wide foyer with iron spindles. Formal dining room, as well as a flex room that can be used as an office space or play area. The downstairs bedroom suite has its own bathroom and a large walk-in closet.

The massive owner's suite upstairs also offers a spacious sitting area, stone tiles in the bathroom, his and hers vanities, separate shower, large tub, and two spacious walk-in closets.

This home is the epitome of convenience meeting a functionality galore. Did I mention that it is located next to Fort Gordon gate 2 and in the highly sought-after McCoys Creek subdivision? Shopping centers and restaurants are literally right outside of the subdivision!!

Do not hesitate to schedule your viewing of this property and make it your next home.
